---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../data/site";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
	<section
		class="py-32 lg:py-52 bg-gold-900 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[60vh] border-b border-brand-800/45"
	>
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<h1
				class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-primary-50 tracking-tighter uppercase leading-[0.9] mb-8"
			>
				BUILD CAPABILITY.<br /><span class="text-primary-500"
					>LIVE WITH PURPOSE.</span
				>
			</h1>
			<p
				class="text-2xl text-gray-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto italic border-l-2 border-primary-500 pl-6 text-left"
			>
				"Excellence is not a single act, but a habit built through
				consistent, faith-aligned discipline."
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-32 bg-brand-900/75">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
			<h2
				class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-50 mb-12 uppercase tracking-wide border-b border-primary-600/30 pb-4 inline-block"
			>
				The Mission
			</h2>
			<div
				class="prose prose-invert prose-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light"
			>
				<p>
					{siteConfig.name} was not created to make you feel good. It
					was created to make you capable. Specifically, capable of
					building the kind of life that aligns with your faith,
					serves your community, and demands disciplined execution.
				</p>
				<p>
					Look around you. We are living in an era of unprecedented
					comfort and unprecedented distraction. The modern world is
					engineered to hook your attention, weaken your habits, and
					sediment your ambition. Scrolling, binge-watching, junk
					food, cheap pleasure — these are not random accidents. They
					are obstacles in the path of your potential.
				</p>
				<p>
					Too many Muslims are losing this battle. They are drifting
					through life, medicating anxiety with cheap entertainment,
					and wondering why they feel empty despite being comfortable.
				</p>
				<p>
					Our mission is simple: <strong class="text-primary-50"
						>To provide the antidote.</strong
					> We exist to pull you out of the seductive comfort of mediocrity
					and into the clarity of high performance — rooted in Islamic
					values, grounded in evidence, and practical in application.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-32 bg-gold-900 border-y border-brand-800/45">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
			<div class="text-right mb-12">
				<h2
					class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-50 uppercase tracking-wide border-b border-primary-600/30 pb-4 inline-block"
				>
					The System
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div
				class="prose prose-invert prose-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-light text-right"
			>
				<p>
					Motivation is garbage. It is a feeling, and feelings are
					fickle. You cannot build a legacy on how you feel on a
					Tuesday morning when it's raining and you're tired.
				</p>
				<p>
					The amateur relies on inspiration. The professional relies
					on systems. A system is a set of behaviors, protocols, and
					environments that make the desired outcome inevitable,
					regardless of how you feel.
				</p>
				<p>
					{siteConfig.name} is a comprehensive operating system for
					the Muslim experience. We don't just tell you to "be
					confident" — we give you specific social scripts and body
					language protocols that signal competence. We don't just tell
					you to "get in shape" — we give you the exact training and
					nutrition frameworks that optimize health within Islamic
					guidelines.
				</p>
				<p>
					We break down the vague concept of success into concrete,
					actionable verticals: Health, Mindset, Social, Wealth, and
					Skill. Each of these is a machine. You are the mechanic. Our
					job is to hand you the wrench.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-32 bg-brand-900/75">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
			<div class="text-center mb-24">
				<h2
					class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-primary-50 mb-6 uppercase tracking-tight"
				>
					Our Methodology
				</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					The algorithm for self-transcendence.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div
					class="bg-gold-900 p-10 border-l-4 border-primary-600 relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-brand-900/72 transition-colors"
				>
					<span
						class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl font-black text-primary-50/5 group-hover:text-primary-500/10 transition-colors"
						>01</span
					>
					<h3
						class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-50 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider"
					>
						Analyze
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
						We strip a problem down to its first principles. We
						ignore tradition and dogma. We only ask: "What is the
						biological or psychological mechanism at play?"
					</p>
				</div>

				<div
					class="bg-gold-900 p-10 border-l-4 border-primary-600 relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-brand-900/72 transition-colors"
				>
					<span
						class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl font-black text-primary-50/5 group-hover:text-primary-500/10 transition-colors"
						>02</span
					>
					<h3
						class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-50 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider"
					>
						Optimize
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
						We design a protocol to exploit that mechanism. This is
						where scientific literature meets field testing. We
						formulate the "Minimum Effective Dose" for maximum
						results.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div
					class="bg-gold-900 p-10 border-l-4 border-primary-600 relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-brand-900/72 transition-colors"
				>
					<span
						class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl font-black text-primary-50/5 group-hover:text-primary-500/10 transition-colors"
						>03</span
					>
					<h3
						class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-50 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider"
					>
						Automate
					</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
						We turn the protocol into a habit. We build the
						environment so that adherence is automatic. Thinking is
						expensive; habits are free. We make excellence improved.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-40 bg-gold-900 border-t border-brand-800/45">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<h2
				class="text-5xl font-black text-primary-50 mb-10 tracking-tighter uppercase"
			>
				Are you <span class="text-primary-500">capable</span> of more?
			</h2>
			<a
				href="/"
				class="inline-block px-12 py-5 border border-primary-500 text-primary-50 hover:bg-primary-600 hover:text-primary-50 font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transition-all duration-300 text-sm"
			>
				Explore The Protocols
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
